commit.message:
Broad the horizon of python versions within the matrix (#185)

* test whether other python3 versions work

* change python versions in CI

* bump python 3.6 version

* pyenv-action v11

* ignore python versions < 3.6

* skip patch version

* temporarily disable python versions 3.8 and 3.11

* strings and ordering

* github actions: use checkout@main and gabrielfalcao/pyenv-action@main

em
passos seguintes

* @%24%24%24 z1 v3

* github actions: use gabrelafalcao/pyenv-action@v12

* alias tests to test and add tests to .PHONY

* a bit of order

* fix exception-checking when applying callback missing context

* run pytest prior to nosetests and delete .coverage before running tests

* github actions: temporarily disable nosetests-tetsts
